<c.bg_transparent>And you,</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:20:46.912 --> 00:20:50.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, um...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't mind my asking that is,</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:20:50.582 --> 00:20:52.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You... You are...?</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:20:52.125 --> 00:20:55.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Mr. Pabst's new secretary,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Darlene Kursky.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:20:55.545 --> 00:20:56.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which one of youse wrote this?</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:20:57.506 --> 00:20:58.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:20:58.757 --> 00:21:00.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You? Surprised?</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:21:00.717 --> 00:21:04.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... It's the best thing I've read</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Since </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>the puppet masters.</i></c.bg_transparent>

316
00:21:04.596 --> 00:21:05.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I read a lot of science fiction.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:21:06.348 --> 00:21:09.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bless you, my child.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The world needs more people like you.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:21:09.393 --> 00:21:13.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This story is really...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's... It's... Um... Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:21:14.022 --> 00:21:15.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How should I put it?</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:21:15.732 --> 00:21:17.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's... It's very...</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:21:17.859 --> 00:21:20.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Impressive?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:21:20.529 --> 00:21:22.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a damn fine piece</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of writing is what it is.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:21:23.490 --> 00:21:26.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> deep space nine</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> is a very</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>intriguing title.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:21:26.785 --> 00:21:27.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very admirable.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:21:28.078 --> 00:21:29.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The master of understatement.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:21:29.705 --> 00:21:32.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What he really means is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He wishes he had half your talent.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:21:33.250 --> 00:21:34.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KAY: You know what, Benny?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:21:34.751 --> 00:21:37.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I like this major. She's a tough cookie.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:21:37.796 --> 00:21:41.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Science fiction needs more strong women.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm always saying that, aren't I?</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:21:41.717 --> 00:21:42.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ad nauseam, dear.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:21:43.218 --> 00:21:46.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>These Cardassians...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I like the way you described them,</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:21:46.638 --> 00:21:47.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Especially the neck ridges.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:21:48.265 --> 00:21:51.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to do some sketches,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>make a nice cover.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:21:51.977 --> 00:21:53.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't waste your time.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:21:53.395 --> 00:21:55.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You, get back to work. You, too, Roy.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:21:56.023 --> 00:21:58.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Douglas, you're not going to tell us</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:21:58.191 --> 00:22:00.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You don't like this story.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, I like it.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:22:00.277 --> 00:22:03.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's very good.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>But you know I can't print it.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:22:03.447 --> 00:22:05.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Why not?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, come on, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:22:05.866 --> 00:22:07.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your hero's a Negro Captain,</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:22:07.784 --> 00:22:10.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The head of a space station,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Christ's sake.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:22:10.662 --> 00:22:11.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong with that?</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:22:12.164 --> 00:22:14.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>People won't accept it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's not believable.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:18.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And men from mars are?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-PABST: Stay out of this, Herb.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:22:18.587 --> 00:22:22.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, Benny, I am a magazine editor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I am not a crusader.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:22:23.008 --> 00:22:26.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not here to change the world.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm here to put out a magazine.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:22:26.219 --> 00:22:28.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That means I have to answer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the publisher,</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:22:28.722 --> 00:22:31.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The national distributors,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the wholesalers,</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:22:31.308 --> 00:22:34.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and none of them are going to want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>To put this story on the newsstand.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:22:34.895 --> 00:22:36.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For all we know, it could cause</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a race riot.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:22:37.272 --> 00:22:39.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations, Douglas.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:22:40.233 --> 00:22:45.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's the most imbecilic attempt</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>To rationalize personal cowardice</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:22:45.655 --> 00:22:46.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That I've ever heard.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:22:47.115 --> 00:22:48.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh. He's angry now.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:22:48.784 --> 00:22:51.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Huh! Herb's been angry</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ever since Josef Stalin died.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:22:51.995 --> 00:22:54.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's that supposed to mean?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You know exactly what it means.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:22:54.748 --> 00:22:56.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You calling me a red?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Easy, easy.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:22:56.708 --> 00:23:00.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Calm down, dear boy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We're writers, not vikings.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:23:01.088 --> 00:23:04.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to stand here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and let some craven fascist call me</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:23:04.674 --> 00:23:06.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HERB: a pinko and get away with it.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:23:06.968 --> 00:23:08.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Douglas, um...</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:23:08.804 --> 00:23:12.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did you think of, uh... of my story?</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:23:12.390 --> 00:23:16.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I loved it. Albert's got the right idea.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's not interested in Negroes or whites.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:23:16.353 --> 00:23:19.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He writes about robots.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's because he is a robot.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:23:20.357 --> 00:23:21.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No offense, Albert.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:23:22.192 --> 00:23:23.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I...</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:23:23.777 --> 00:23:29.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like robots.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They're very... Uh... Uh, efficient.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:23:30.242 --> 00:23:32.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here. Write me a novella</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>based on this picture.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:23:32.327 --> 00:23:34.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll print it in next month's issue.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:23:34.830 --> 00:23:36.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You do a good job,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you might even get the cover.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:23:36.915 --> 00:23:39.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What about my story?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-The way I see it,</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:23:39.167 --> 00:23:40.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can either burn it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or stick it in a drawer</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:23:41.002 --> 00:23:42.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For the next 50 years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or how ever long it takes</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:23:42.921 --> 00:23:45.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The human race to become color-blind.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want people to read it now.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:23:45.966 --> 00:23:48.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want me to print it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>make the Captain white.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:23:48.927 --> 00:23:49.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not what I wrote!</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:23:50.846 --> 00:23:51.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's your call.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:24:09.447 --> 00:24:11.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry they didn't buy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your story, baby.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:24:11.741 --> 00:24:12.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really I am.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:24:12.909 --> 00:24:16.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you you were wasting your time.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>A colored Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:24:17.122 --> 00:24:19.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only reason</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they'll ever let us in space</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:24:19.666 --> 00:24:21.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is if they need someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to shine their shoes.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:24:22.085 --> 00:24:23.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ain't that right, Cassie?</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:24:23.628 --> 00:24:25.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know, and to be honest.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:24:25.297 --> 00:24:27.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't much care what happens</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a hundred years from now.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:24:28.592 --> 00:24:29.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's today that matters.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:24:30.010 --> 00:24:31.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I've got news for you.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:24:31.636 --> 00:24:34.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Today or 100 years from now,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It don't make a bit of difference.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:24:35.056 --> 00:24:38.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As far as they're concerned,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll always be niggers.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:24:39.060 --> 00:24:41.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Things are going to change. They have to.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:24:41.897 --> 00:24:43.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you keep telling yourself that.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:24:44.107 --> 00:24:45.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe this is all happening for a reason.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:24:46.359 --> 00:24:48.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean maybe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's God's way of telling me</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:24:48.361 --> 00:24:51.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I should quit writing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and go into the restaurant business?</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:24:51.489 --> 00:24:52.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, it's possible.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:24:55.410 --> 00:24:59.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Baby, I know we can make this work for us.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We could be happy.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:24:59.706 --> 00:25:02.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, you don't have to give up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Writing altogether.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:25:02.250 --> 00:25:05.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe you could write something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the Amsterdam news</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:25:05.128 --> 00:25:07.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or... Some other Negro newspaper.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:25:07.964 --> 00:25:11.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not a reporter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a writer. I write fiction,</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:25:12.010 --> 00:25:14.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the Amsterdam news</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is not going to publish stories</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:25:14.888 --> 00:25:17.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>about a space station 400 years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into the future.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:25:20.018 --> 00:25:21.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hear the game last night?</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:25:21.645 --> 00:25:23.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:25:24.981 --> 00:25:27.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't mean to frighten you.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:25:27.776 --> 00:25:30.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't look so good.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You sick or something?</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:25:31.112 --> 00:25:33.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, no, I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You want to lie down in the back?</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:25:33.448 --> 00:25:34.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I... I just need some air.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:25:35.075 --> 00:25:36.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are we still on for tonight?</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:25:37.035 --> 00:25:39.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll pick you up about 10:00.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:25:40.580 --> 00:25:41.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Door shuts )</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:25:41.957 --> 00:25:43.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, what are you doing till 10:00?</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:25:44.709 --> 00:25:46.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Whatever it is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I won't be doing it with you.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:25:56.638 --> 00:25:57.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PREACHER: Hello, brother Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:26:00.183 --> 00:26:01.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you again.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:26:01.851 --> 00:26:03.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand what you want from me.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:26:04.187 --> 00:26:06.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To follow the path of the prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:26:07.232 --> 00:26:09.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Walk with the prophets, brother Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:26:10.443 --> 00:26:11.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Show us the way.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:26:12.153 --> 00:26:13.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>W--what way?</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:26:13.697 --> 00:26:17.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't know what you're talking about.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Write the words, brother Benny...</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:26:17.826 --> 00:26:20.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>PREACHER: The words that will lead</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>us out of the darkness</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:26:20.787 --> 00:26:25.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Onto the path of righteousness!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Write the words, brother Benny!</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:26:26.042 --> 00:26:27.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Write the words!</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:26:53.945 --> 00:26:57.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Playing slow jazz )</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:27:10.003 --> 00:27:10.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, baby.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:27:11.296 --> 00:27:12.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, hey, hey.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:27:13.173 --> 00:27:14.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You forgot all about our date.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:27:15.300 --> 00:27:18.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ohh... Our date. I'm sorry. I was working.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:27:20.764 --> 00:27:23.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ben Sisko?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Isn't that your colored Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:27:23.391 --> 00:27:24.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:27:25.060 --> 00:27:27.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you writing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another one of those stories?</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:27:27.437 --> 00:27:30.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You couldn't sell the last one.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what makes you think this one</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:27:30.482 --> 00:27:31.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be any different?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:27:32.108 --> 00:27:34.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It probably won't be,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:27:35.653 --> 00:27:39.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's what I've got to do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Right now, what you've got to do is eat.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:27:40.158 --> 00:27:42.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not hungry. ( Yawning )</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:27:42.952 --> 00:27:44.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What time is it anyway?</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:27:46.956 --> 00:27:50.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's after midnight.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I should be getting home to bed.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:27:51.002 --> 00:27:54.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But before I go, what do you say</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we take a spin on the dance floor?</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:27:55.298 --> 00:27:56.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Okay.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:28:07.310 --> 00:28:10.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm. Feels good, doesn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:28:11.064 --> 00:28:13.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could stay like this forever.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:28:13.817 --> 00:28:15.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm, me, too. It's times like these</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:28:15.860 --> 00:28:18.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That I wish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'd never heard of the Dominion.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:28:18.196 --> 00:28:19.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Dominion?</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:28:19.531 --> 00:28:21.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:28:21.241 --> 00:28:23.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said something about the Dominion.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:28:25.495 --> 00:28:26.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it, Ben?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:28:27.205 --> 00:28:29.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:28:29.207 --> 00:28:30.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:28:30.750 --> 00:28:32.085 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think I'm losing my mind.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:28:35.713 --> 00:28:40.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me what's wrong.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm starting to see things from my story.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:28:40.427 --> 00:28:43.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's as if I'm becoming</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this Captain Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:28:44.222 --> 00:28:46.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Okay, baby,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you just need to get some rest.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:28:46.516 --> 00:28:49.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right. It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:28:49.436 --> 00:28:51.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm with you. I'm with you, baby.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:28:51.479 --> 00:28:54.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just take it easy. Shh.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:28:59.446 --> 00:29:01.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you lost your mind?</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:29:02.073 --> 00:29:04.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been asking myself the same question.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:29:04.325 --> 00:29:06.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I give you a novella to write,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I even offer you a shot at the cover.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:29:06.953 --> 00:29:08.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Three weeks later instead of a novella,</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:29:08.580 --> 00:29:10.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You come back with six stories,</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:29:10.290 --> 00:29:12.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Six </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>sequels </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>to a story</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I refused to publish</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:29:12.917 --> 00:29:17.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the first place. So I guess the answer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>To the question we've both been asking</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:29:17.464 --> 00:29:21.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is, yeah, you are certifiable.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think you should print your own stories</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:29:22.260 --> 00:29:26.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Through a private publishing house.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>A nice, elegant volume 50 to 100 copies.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:29:26.681 --> 00:29:28.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a great idea.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:29:28.308 --> 00:29:30.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, might as well write it in chalk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the sidewalk.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:29:30.268 --> 00:29:32.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>More people would read it that way.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:29:32.187 --> 00:29:37.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got an idea.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Why not make them, you know, a, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:29:37.400 --> 00:29:40.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A d--dream?</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:29:42.739 --> 00:29:43.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:29:43.740 --> 00:29:45.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just make the ending</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:29:45.825 --> 00:29:48.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of your first story</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>deep space nine </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>a...</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:29:50.163 --> 00:29:50.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dream.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:29:52.665 --> 00:29:54.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would that make a difference?</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:29:54.542 --> 00:29:55.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:29:57.545 --> 00:29:59.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That depends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On what?</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:29:59.297 --> 00:30:00.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On who's doing the dreaming.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:30:00.965 --> 00:30:04.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, obviously someone, uh...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Someone without a lot of hope.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:30:05.136 --> 00:30:08.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A--a shoeshine boy, a convict...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Someone dreaming of a better future.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:30:10.058 --> 00:30:10.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:30:11.768 --> 00:30:12.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Negro.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:30:13.019 --> 00:30:17.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, well, I suppose he'd have to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if he was dreaming about a Negro Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:30:17.607 --> 00:30:19.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HERB: Hold on.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:30:19.317 --> 00:30:23.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Making it a dream guts the story.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Shut up, Herb!</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:30:23.488 --> 00:30:24.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it makes it more poignant.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:30:25.031 --> 00:30:27.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about the other Sisko stories?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You can't make them all a dream.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:30:28.034 --> 00:30:31.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let him get this published,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then worry about the others.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:30:31.913 --> 00:30:32.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you think, Benny?</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:30:35.458 --> 00:30:36.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think...</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:30:38.169 --> 00:30:40.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's better than chalk on the sidewalk.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:30:43.091 --> 00:30:43.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can I play?</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:30:44.884 --> 00:30:47.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, Jimmy, I got great news.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We are headed for the stars.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:30:47.887 --> 00:30:49.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, sure, whatever.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:30:49.556 --> 00:30:50.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, come on.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll buy you lunch.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:30:50.849 --> 00:30:51.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll tell you all about it.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:30:51.808 --> 00:30:53.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Later. I got some business</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to take care of.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:30:53.768 --> 00:30:54.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What kind of business?</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:30:55.061 --> 00:30:56.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Big time. That's all I'm saying.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:30:56.896 --> 00:30:58.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, hold it. Hold it.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:30:58.523 --> 00:30:59.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:30:59.774 --> 00:31:00.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry about it.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:31:00.817 --> 00:31:02.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's cool, I got it under control.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Huh?</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:31:03.444 --> 00:31:04.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see you around.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:31:07.657 --> 00:31:09.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bottom of the seventh, I'm up again.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:31:09.701 --> 00:31:12.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>O-2 fast ball... bam!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Into the left field bleachers.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:31:13.621 --> 00:31:15.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Had to be 400 feet.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:31:15.707 --> 00:31:18.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know all about it, Willie.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I read the newspaper.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:31:18.835 --> 00:31:20.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, but you got to admit...</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:31:20.837 --> 00:31:22.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They don't tell it like I tell it.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:31:23.840 --> 00:31:25.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BENNY: Hey, Cassie!</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:31:28.386 --> 00:31:29.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Giggles )</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:31:29.304 --> 00:31:31.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WILLIE: Hey, man, did you hear</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the game last night?</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:31:31.264 --> 00:31:32.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
