<c.bg_transparent>I have no choice, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:38:07.618 --> 00:38:09.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's his decision.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:38:10.579 --> 00:38:13.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you can't fire me.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:38:13.624 --> 00:38:17.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I quit. To hell with you...</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:38:18.462 --> 00:38:20.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And to hell with Stone.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:38:20.840 --> 00:38:22.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try to stay calm, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:38:22.258 --> 00:38:26.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! I'm tired of being calm.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Calm never got me a damn thing.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:38:26.554 --> 00:38:27.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm warning you, Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:38:27.555 --> 00:38:30.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't stop this,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to call the police.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:38:30.141 --> 00:38:31.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You go ahead! Call them!</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:38:32.601 --> 00:38:35.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Call anybody you want.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They can't do anything to me.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:38:36.022 --> 00:38:38.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not anymore... And nor can any of you!</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:38:43.946 --> 00:38:48.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... Am a human being, damn it.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:38:49.910 --> 00:38:55.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can deny me all you want...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>But you cannot deny Ben Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:38:55.583 --> 00:38:56.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He exists.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:38:57.084 --> 00:39:02.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That future, that space station,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all those people, they exist in here.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:39:03.466 --> 00:39:09.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In my mind. I created it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And every one of you know it.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:39:09.430 --> 00:39:10.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You read it.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:39:11.307 --> 00:39:14.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's here. You get what I'm telling you?</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:39:15.186 --> 00:39:19.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can pulp a story,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but you cannot destroy an idea.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:39:19.774 --> 00:39:22.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you understand?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That's ancient knowledge.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:39:22.401 --> 00:39:25.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You cannot destroy an idea.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:39:27.281 --> 00:39:31.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That future I created it, and it's real!</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:39:31.952 --> 00:39:34.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you understand?</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:39:34.622 --> 00:39:40.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is real! I created it, and it's real!</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:39:40.378 --> 00:39:44.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's real. Oh, god!</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:39:44.924 --> 00:39:46.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Weeping )</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:39:58.521 --> 00:39:59.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PARAMEDIC: Easy...</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:40:13.244 --> 00:40:14.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One... two... three.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:40:35.975 --> 00:40:37.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rest easy, brother Benny.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:40:38.060 --> 00:40:40.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have walked in the path</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:40:41.147 --> 00:40:43.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is no greater glory.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:40:43.816 --> 00:40:45.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me, please.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:40:46.193 --> 00:40:47.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who am I?</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:40:47.987 --> 00:40:49.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you know?</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:40:49.822 --> 00:40:50.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:40:52.074 --> 00:40:55.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the dreamer...</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:40:55.494 --> 00:40:57.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the dream.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:41:13.471 --> 00:41:15.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KASIDY: Ben.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:41:16.474 --> 00:41:17.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ben?</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:41:27.860 --> 00:41:30.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How long was I out?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Only for a few minutes.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:41:31.280 --> 00:41:33.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seemed like forever to me.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:41:34.283 --> 00:41:35.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's odd.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:41:35.993 --> 00:41:38.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somehow your neural patterns</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have returned to normal.</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:41:38.746 --> 00:41:41.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That's good, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, it's very good.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:41:41.499 --> 00:41:44.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just don't understand how it happened.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:41:51.425 --> 00:41:53.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you feeling, son?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:41:53.802 --> 00:41:54.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm okay.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:41:56.388 --> 00:41:57.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm done packing.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:41:58.891 --> 00:42:01.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Transport leaves at 8:00 in the morning.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:42:02.311 --> 00:42:04.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish you could stay longer.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:42:05.147 --> 00:42:07.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got to get back to the restaurant.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:42:07.983 --> 00:42:10.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My customers have never</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>gone this long without me.</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:42:12.738 --> 00:42:15.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The question is what are you going to do?</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:42:18.536 --> 00:42:23.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only thing I can do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Stay here and finish the job I started,</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:42:24.708 --> 00:42:26.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And if I fail...</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:42:26.418 --> 00:42:31.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"I have fought the good fight...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have finished the course...</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:42:32.299 --> 00:42:34.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have kept the faith."</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:42:35.928 --> 00:42:37.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never known you to quote</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the bible.</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:42:38.430 --> 00:42:40.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm full of surprises, aren't I?</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:42:42.977 --> 00:42:44.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And so are you.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:42:45.646 --> 00:42:49.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sounds like that dream</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you had... Helped you sort things out.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:42:50.526 --> 00:42:51.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose it did...</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:42:53.279 --> 00:42:55.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I have begun to wonder.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:42:56.615 --> 00:42:58.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it wasn't a dream?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:42:59.535 --> 00:43:03.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if this life we're leading,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all of this...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:43:04.582 --> 00:43:11.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and me, everything...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What if all of this is the illusion?</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:43:12.548 --> 00:43:14.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a scary thought.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:43:15.551 --> 00:43:16.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know. I know.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:43:17.720 --> 00:43:19.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But maybe, just maybe...</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:43:20.222 --> 00:43:21.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benny isn't the dream.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:43:22.349 --> 00:43:23.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:43:24.310 --> 00:43:28.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we're nothing more than figments</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his imagination.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:43:30.733 --> 00:43:31.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For all we know...</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:43:33.652 --> 00:43:34.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At this very moment,</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:43:35.613 --> 00:43:40.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somewhere far beyond</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all those distant stars...</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:43:41.535 --> 00:43:42.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benny Russell...</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:43:43.829 --> 00:43:45.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is dreaming of us.</c.bg_transparent>

